data.description: Don't wait for next summer to enjoy your own heated saltwater pool and the weather is perfect for the hot tub! This 4 bed 3 full bath home located in Park Hampton subdivision is move in ready and over 3000 square feet.Split floorplan offers privacy and a guestroom ensuite is perfect for teenager or in-law.Kitchen is large with ample custom cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and a huge pantry with wooden shelves. Features include stacked stone fireplace, screened in porch, stamped concrete, privacy fence, 3 car garage, dedicated office.New hardwood floors in 2022 and fresh paint. Conveniently located to Huntsville Hospital, Jones Valley 20 minutes to Redstone Arsenal.
